1 MAINE OFFICE OF COMMUNITY AFFAIRS
2 Reimbursement - Municipal Housing Data Reporting N533
3 Initiative: Provides ongoing funds to reimburse municipalities with 4,000 or more residents
4 for the cost of preparing an annual report on certain housing data, including data on
5 residential building permits, dwelling units permitted and demolished, certificates of
6 occupancy or other approvals of housing units issued, as well as certain affordability data.
